    "In this subsection, the authors use to verify the content from publisher signature.",
    "Table 2 provide summary of the the given literature.",
    "Ribeiro et al. (2014) suggest a technique termed \"CCNCheck\".",
    "In the propose scheme, the NDN routers probabilistically verify the signature of content.",
